		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'd like to see the NES-JOINT adapter for buying (if possible). I don't think it's easy to find on MercadoLivre, since most of 60-72 adapters have no chip inside to make a Famicom cart playable in a NES.<br /><br />I got the F1 Race cart, but I'm unable to test it, since my famiclone has a broken reset button, and my NES doesn't run it with the adapter I have.

		

