		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I usually take my front loader NES apart if I want to use the gyromite adapter. Famicom games won't really fit in there otherwise.<br /><br />As an adapter though I think it's good, and the board is accessible so it's easy to modify. I added an extra wire for the audio expansions.

		

